Boaz Weinstein

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Boaz Weinstein


Born
1973


Nationality
United States


Alma mater
B.A. University of Michigan


Occupation
Founder of Saba Capital Management


